df <- df %>% 
  mutate(x5 = 1 - (x1 + x2 + x3 + x4),
         w = x2 / (x3 + x4),
         z = (x1 + x2) / (x5 + x4),
         t = v1 * v2)
df <- df %>% 
  mutate(y = boot::logit(output)) 
df <- df %>% 
  mutate(outcome = ifelse(output < 0.33, 'event', 'non_event'),
         outcome = factor(outcome, levels = c("event", "non_event")))
